Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:03.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! I'm reporting live from E-Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can everyone see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's an amusement \Npark in the middle of Edolas's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How whacked-out is this King anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all fun, either. You'll \Nencounter many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone check out all the \Ndifferent kinds of attractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:57.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world which is losing its magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:02:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people live their lives with \Nmagic as a limited commodity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All Wizard Guilds have been disbanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are still those \Nwho resist and continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And their name is the Dark Guild, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the curtain has risen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:24.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,on the battle between the Fairy Tail \Nwizards that came from Earthland,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Magic Regiments of the Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you return to your cells, or die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Boy, we don't have \Nto give them the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finished extracting \Nthe dragon's magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:03:00.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Code ETD is a success, we'll have \Nno need for the Dragon Slayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You Earthlanders with no concept of \Nthe value of magic will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Life!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An ice shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is Earthland magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't use tools, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's flames around his legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your "friends" will mix with Extalia's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and become an eternal supply of magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:24.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you still blabbing about \Nthat? I said we ain't gonna let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sinking into the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that'll hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell's Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shooting out the rail it's going along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He sounds like he's enjoying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:05:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, my weapon, the Command Tact, can cause \Nall the attractions here to freely move at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you can move 'em all you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I gotta do is bust 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good, you imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than one Hell's Coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it plays a beautiful \Nsymphony, which I conduct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This attraction considers the safety \Nof its guests its number one priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:38.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using enough magic power, the Hell's Coaster \Ncan accelerate to 10 times normal speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who you are, 5 \Nminutes riding that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been more than 10 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's with this guy? He's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't going well over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing so well here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, pull Natsu out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is pretty brave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:43.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Flying Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:52.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had that kind of magic, wouldn't \Nit have been better if you rescued him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then no one would be around to kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Death Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice magic, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I may be at an advantage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:33.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This weapon, Rossa Espada, \Nsoftens anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is really, truly, unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these things? \NThey won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said pull it together, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:18.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}thanks{\i0} for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:34.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Edolas's magic! Like, whoa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this wonderful magic \Nwill be gone pretty soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even wanna think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you'll kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll kill my friends and the \NExceeds for your convenience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be sacrificed for the \Nsake of our eternal magic supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Exceeds are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's more important than \Nwhether or not there's magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's life!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Water Bearer, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Aquarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot control this water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you once already... Everything \Nin this amusement park is my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, all the preparations \Nhave been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reached the final stage of Code ETD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power we extracted \Nfrom the Dragon Slayers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,can be thought of as giant chains enabling \Nyou to move the floating islands at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:09.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once the floating islands \Nare under your control,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:15.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all you need to do is simply ram that \Nlacrima into those damn cats' kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:21.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and the magic \Npower will fuse together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and an eternity of magic power \Nwill rain down on our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Edolas magic spell, Dragon Chain Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:39.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A device which utilizes the \Nmagic power of dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Presently, it cannot be used as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to activate the \NDragon Chain Cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you \Nnot to run around near the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily is there on that lacrima island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Earthland magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is quite intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a guy that's actually near my level!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be enjoying yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you're heavy, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not as heavy as Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you should be sayin' that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's gonna pulverize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Salamander's cat, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look forward to fightin' in \Nthe air when I find my own cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Charging Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Ma'am, reactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But damn, that's one big sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we measure it this way, \Nit's 4 Panther Lily's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a crap about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chatting during a battle? \NYou are overly confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He chopped off some of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:25.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't just big... The guy who's \Nwielding it is skilled as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:29.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you nothing more than rust \Non my Great Sword, Master Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But you know, rust is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Gajeel's iron, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:54.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you activate the plan now, \NLily will be caught up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, he will be a martyr to \Nour great Kingdom's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Lily to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what happens to that damn Exceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have always loved to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I loved to watch you run around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand the key over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bydo, after her! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had my feet feel such pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I want everlasting magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want Lily to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey, where's Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, here! I'm in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you in a a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I realized it, I was in this dark, \Ncramped place and couldn't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing in that outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Costume actor box...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, dress up in a wonderful outfit and set \Nforth on your journey to Fairy Tale land!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a dial here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Righto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playin' around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, {\i1}you{\i0} stop playin' around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go, Earthland wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being all hard-boiled in that \Ngetup doesn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and change me back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a {\i1}great{\i0} idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, were they blown far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Earthland wizards talk big \Nand act big, but they ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My sexy seduction plan was a giant flop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell are these monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Monster Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an attraction that gives you a \Npeek at the school days of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just let me change \Nback into my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hurry up and save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! How can you be so incredibly unsexy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what his problem is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought it was such a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just gotta go straight at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really plan on fighting me \Nhere in this Monster Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my favorite place, \NI'll have you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it? Well, I like this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mummy Bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:48.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every monster in Monster \NAcademy is my soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, whoa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames from his entire body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Franken Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Troops, assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:45.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really win against these monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, monsters? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these monsters?! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where're the monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're seriously injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, wait, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... This person \Nis the girl from Earthland...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, I can't give her the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give me the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Key?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why is he after my keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give any of them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's confused about something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'll beat him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where'd Lucy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran off yelling somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she playing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray and the guy with the \Nchin ain't around, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chin person tripped on his chin \Nand went flying and he gave chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chin on the chin did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Great River \Nof Stars is for Pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple, the chin person \Nwent flying, like swoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:21.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A chin can fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like \Nonly the chin is flying!
